item.title: Solar Eclipse
item.description: First time in my life experiencing a total solar eclipse, and holy shit was that magical. Unfortunately I didn’t have a zoom lens so this photo hopefully captures more accurately what the real experience is like seeing the sun through eclipse glasses. A few weeks before the eclipse, I suggested to one of my good friends that we organize a small trip to see the total solar eclipse. That small group ended up becoming 10 or so people, and we struggled for a while coming to a decision on where to go.
